description.en:
Reinventing the retail business and customer relationship.

Netkoin (NTK) is an ERC20 token based on the Ethereum blockchain. The NTK token will be used to power Netkoin’s universal rewards system on Netkoin’s location based mobile application and business management platform.

Netkoin’s location based mobile advertising application aims to make retail shopping relevant and rewarding for customers based on their location. The mobile application will contain numerous features and filters in order to provide the customer with a personalized retail shopping experience, while maintaining the highest level of user’s data security and privacy.

Netkoin’s business management platform will be utilized by retail stores to enable business owners to manage their stores advertising on the Netkoin mobile application. Businesses can integrate their store’s social media content, providing them with a single place of advertising their businesses content with shoppers. Therefore reducing content marketing management by the retail business marketing team.

status_updates.description: We are pleased to announce a new version of Netkoin's mobile app is now available on the Google Play Store: https://bit.ly/3jMxh08. You can now claim NTK for multiple cryptocurrencies including Binance Coin, Dogecoin, Litecoin, Polkadot, and more!

We are pleased to announce a new version of Netkoin's mobile app will be launching Monday! This update will enable users to start claiming the NTK they have earned for other cryptocurrencies like Ethereum. New offers (tasks) have also been added in this version.

We are pleased to announce our roadmap for the development of Netkoin's mobile app for the next few months. Some of the features outlined in this post will be launching next week!

Read the Roadmap here: https://netkoin.medium.com/mobile-app-development-roadmap-13b117484e27

Great news iOS users!

The new version of Netkoin's mobile app will be available for iOS devices in December. You will be able to earn $NTK by completing microtasks such as playing games, participating in surveys, and watching ads!

Official launch date will be announced soon.

Since the launch of the new version of our mobile app, millions of NTK have already been earned by users completing microtasks. We are excited by the success of the launch and are pleased to announce we will be adding even more microtasks in an update to the android version soon.

Download app: https://bit.ly/3mJ6vGq
Are you enjoying earning cryptocurrency using the new version of Netkoin's mobile app? Show us your support by rating the app on the Google Play Store here: https://bit.ly/3mJ6vGq

We are pleased to announce the new version of Netkoin's mobile app is now available for download here: https://bit.ly/3mJ6vGq

You can now start earning NTK by completing microtasks including downloading and playing games, watching ads, and participating in surveys.

This version also enables you to claim the NTK you have earned by completing microtasks. When you claim the NTK you have earned you will receive it in the Ethereum wallet you created.
